title: Portable Office 2007
description:
Portable version of MS Office 2007.

This is a simpler edition of Office that can be loaded onto USB and be carried anywhere.

This includes Portable:
- Microsoft Office Word 2007
- Microsoft Office Powerpoint 2007
- Microsoft Office Access 2007
- Microsoft Office Excel 2007
- Microsoft Office Picture Manager 2007
- Microsoft Office Clip Organiser 2007
- Microsoft Office Diagnostics 2007

very handy, especially if you have a file that is saved in 2007 format and the computer you are using doesn\&#039;t have \&#039;07.
